title: Sunes jul
resume: Sunes jul was the 1991 Swedish Television Christmas Calendar. In 2004, it was later released to DVD. In 2007, it was voted the third best Julkalender ever in Aftonbladet. It is based on the books series about the boy Sune by Anders Jacobsson and Sören Olsson.
